---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RelatedPosts from "../components/RelatedPosts.astro";

const metaTitle = "What is a car swivel seat?";
const metaDescription =
  "How 360° swivel seats make car entry and exit easier, safer, and more comfortable for people with disabilities or seniors.";
const currentSlug = "what-is-a-car-swivel-seat";
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.endsWith("/") ? import.meta.env.BASE_URL : `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/`;
const ogImage = `${base}logo.png`;
---

<BaseLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} headerVariant="solid">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta property="og:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta property="og:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta property="og:image" content={ogImage} />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content={metaTitle} />
    <meta name="twitter:description" content={metaDescription} />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content={ogImage} />
  </Fragment>

  <article class="article">
    <header class="article-head">
      <p class="article-date">June 8, 2023 · by vivek</p>
      <h1>What is a car swivel seat?</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="article-grid">
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>
          A car swivel seat is a type of car seat that allows the seat to rotate 360 degrees. This can be helpful for
          people who have difficulty getting in and out of the car, such as people with disabilities or the elderly.
        </p>

        <p>
          Swivel seats are becoming increasingly popular as more people become aware of the benefits they offer. Here are
          some of the benefits of using a car swivel seat:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Easier access to the car: Swivel seats make it easier for people to get in and out of the car, which can be helpful for people with disabilities or the elderly.</li>
          <li>Increased safety: Swivel seats can help to reduce the risk of falls and injuries, especially for people who have difficulty getting in and out of the car.</li>
          <li>Increased comfort: Swivel seats can provide a more comfortable ride, especially for people who have difficulty sitting for long periods of time.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          If you are considering using a car swivel seat, there are a few things you should keep in mind. First, make sure
          that the seat is compatible with your car. Second, make sure that the seat is the right size for the person who
          will be using it. Third, make sure that the seat is installed properly.
        </p>

        <p>
          Car swivel seats can be a great way to make it easier for people with disabilities or the elderly to get in and
          out of the car. If you are looking for a way to make your car more accessible, a car swivel seat is a great
          option.
        </p>

        <p>
          Here are some additional tips for choosing and using a car swivel seat:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Choose a seat that is the right size for the person who will be using it. The seat should be wide enough for the person to sit comfortably and deep enough for the person’s legs to reach the floor.</li>
          <li>Choose a seat that is easy to install and use. The seat should be easy for the person to get in and out of, and it should be easy for the caregiver to install and adjust.</li>
          <li>Choose a seat that is made from durable materials. The seat should be able to withstand the wear and tear of everyday use.</li>
          <li>Choose a seat that is safe. The seat should meet all safety standards and should be equipped with a five-point harness.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>
          With careful planning, you can choose the right car swivel seat for your needs and make your car more accessible
          for everyone.
        </p>
      </div>

      <aside class="sidebar" aria-label="Products">
        <div class="products-card">
          <h2>Products</h2>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/nlMO30_RrKc"
                title="TurnPlus video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus</p>
              <p class="product-link">Swivel solution for easier entry/exit.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-electric" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ytQ7nRd8rf4"
                title="TurnPlus Electric video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Electric</p>
              <p class="product-link">Powered swivel seat convenience.</p>
            </div>
          </a>

          <a class="product-card" href="https://www.trueassistech.com/products/turnplus-accelerate" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <div class="video-frame">
              <iframe
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/-bSUnSfkD-8"
                title="TurnPlus Accelerate video"
                loading="lazy"
                allowfullscreen
              ></iframe>
            </div>
            <div class="product-body">
              <p class="product-title">TurnPlus Accelerate</p>
              <p class="product-link">Rapid, smooth swivel assistance.</p>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </article>

  <RelatedPosts currentSlug={currentSlug} />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .article {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .article-head h1 {
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .article-date {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .article-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 1.4fr;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .article-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  h2 {
    color: #451e5d;
    margin: 0.35rem 0 0.15rem;
  }

  p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-body);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }

  .sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 80px;
  }

  .products-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 0.9rem;
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .products-card h2 {
    margin: 0;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-card {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.6rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    background: #f9f9f9;
  }

  .product-card:hover {
    border-color: #451e5d;
  }

  .video-frame {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #000;
  }

  .video-frame iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
  }

  .product-body {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.15rem;
  }

  .product-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #451e5d;
  }

  .product-link {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .article-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
